text:
Producer-san!
Is today's work already over?

Yeah, I'm free after this.
─Want to go on an adventure?

Oh, you're right.
Are you in elementary school? That's rare.

Yes!
It's a bit strange because my school is different.

I found the same thing!
The person holding a flag at the crosswalk!

Oh...! Yeah, parents take turns doing
that to protect the children in the city.
